|GKO================================================================
                       |CKOCrinoslong
|GKO================================================================

|YKOCrinoslong allows you to change the long description
of your crinos form. This is what the players will
see when they 'look' at you. Please keep descriptions
consistent with the crinos form. Inappropriate
descriptions will be removed.

|RKOSyntax: |YKBcrinoslong <description>
